{"type":"message","id":"1795c100","parentId":"2a518e43","timestamp":"2026-03-06T01:27:36.057Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about the x402 payment integration status for Parse. Let me route this properly.\n\nAccording to AGENTS.md routing table:\n- payment/billing/pricing/x402/protocol/SDK → temujin\n\nThis is clearly a payment/protocol question about x402 implementation, so I should route to Temujin (the code/build/protocol agent).\n\nBut first, let me check if there's any existing information in the workspace that I should know about. The MEMORY.md mentions:\n- \"x402 payment integration for Parse\" under Active Projects\n- Parse Monetization is an active project\n\nSince this is asking about the status of a payment/protocol implementation, this is Temujin's domain. I should route this to Temujin via message().\n\nActually, wait - let me re-read the routing rules. The user is asking for STATUS - which could be:\n1. A simple status check (I could look at files)\n2. A technical implementation question (temujin)\n\nLooking at AGENTS.md:\n- temujin: Code, builds, bugs, APIs, deploy, design, architecture, payment, protocol, SDK\n\nThe question is about \"x402 pay as you go implementation for parse for agents\" - this is payment + protocol related. I should route to Temujin.\n\nLet me send a message to the temujin session asking for a status update.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Let me route this to Temujin for the payment/protocol implementation status."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_50487981a63b48359a6fbac7","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","target":"temujin","message":"Status request from human: What's the current status of the x402 pay-as-you-go implementation for Parse for agents?\n\nPlease provide:\n1. Current implementation state (deployed/in-progress/blocked)\n2. What's working\n3. What's pending or blocked\n4. Next steps\n\nThis is a payment/protocol domain question so routing to you."}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai-coding","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":66,"output":403,"cacheRead":19136,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19605,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772760434675}}
