{"type":"message","id":"2ceda9cb","parentId":"bcd24451","timestamp":"2026-03-06T01:30:26.993Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting - the ARCHITECTURE.md doesn't have any x402 mentions. Let me search more specifically for x402 in the project files.\n\nAlso, I notice that PARSE_FOR_AGENTS.md mentions:\n- \"Credit/billing system with Stripe\"\n- \"credits_used: 3\"\n\nSo it seems like the current plan uses credits + Stripe, not x402.\n\nLet me search more specifically for x402 in the project.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Let me search more specifically for x402 mentions in the project:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0db41ccef09c42e69c22574c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -rn \"x402\\|402\" ~/projects/parse-github/ --include=\"*.ts\" --include=\"*.tsx\" --include=\"*.js\" --include=\"*.md\" --include=\"*.json\" 2>/dev/null | grep -v node_modules | head -30"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5c5e474115454fadbba588e3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/projects/parse-github/src/lib/CLAUDE.md 2>/dev/null | head -100"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai-coding","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":17503,"output":210,"cacheRead":25088,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42801,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772760617987}}
