{"type":"message","id":"c2a99f76","parentId":"b3973c6b","timestamp":"2026-03-06T01:31:29.399Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So the x402 implementation has NOT started. The design is complete but no code has been written - the @x402 packages are not even installed in the project.\n\nLet me provide a comprehensive status report to the user.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"## x402 Pay-As-You-Go Implementation Status\n\n**TL;DR:** Design complete, implementation not started.\n\n### Current State\n\n| Component | Status |\n|-----------|--------|\n| Design Document | COMPLETE |\n| SDK Installation | NOT STARTED |\n| Middleware Integration | NOT STARTED |\n| Wallet Setup | NOT STARTED |\n| Testnet Testing | NOT STARTED |\n\n### Design Summary\n\nThe design document (created today at 17:57) specifies:\n\n**Pricing (USDC on Base L2):**\n- `POST /v1/analyze` - $0.01 (quick) / $0.05 (standard) / $0.15 (deep)\n- `POST /v1/evaluate` - $0.01 per call\n- `POST /v1/chat` - $0.005 per message\n- `GET /v1/analyze/:id`, `/models`, `/pricing` - FREE\n\n**Architecture:**\n- Uses `@x402/hono` SDK (direct fit for Parse's Hono framework)\n- Base L2 network for sub-cent gas fees\n- Coinbase CDP Facilitator for verification/settlement\n- Dual access: x402 payment OR existing API key auth\n\n**Timeline (per design):**\n- Week 1: Core SDK integration + middleware\n- Week 2: Payment tracking + dashboard\n- Week 3: Production launch on Base mainnet\n\n### Blockers\n\n1. Parse for Agents MVP itself is still being scaffolded (pending task in temujin/tasks)\n2. @x402 packages not yet installed in parse-github project\n3. No Base wallet configured\n\n### Next Steps\n\n1. Complete Parse for Agents MVP endpoints first\n2. Install `@x402/hono @x402/core @x402/evm`\n3. Create `src/x402.ts` with middleware config\n4. Set up Base wallet for USDC receipt\n5. Test on Base Sepolia testnet\n6. Deploy to mainnet\n\nWant me to route this to Temujin to begin implementation, or would you like to review the design first?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai-coding","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":372,"output":496,"cacheRead":54016,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54884,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772760669232}}
