{"type":"message","id":"da614447","parentId":"9c933c24","timestamp":"2026-03-06T01:32:47.446Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_a18f4bf6265b45c589d81460","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\ntask_id: high-1772671400\npriority: high\ncreated: 2026-03-05T19:10:00-05:00\nsource: hourly-reflection\n---\n\n# Task: Apply Watchdog False-Positive Fix\n\n## Objective\nApply the 3-line fix to eliminate 35 false-positive stalled_warnings.\n\n## Bug Location\nFile: `scripts/ogedei-watchdog.py`\nLine: ~140\n\n## Fix\n```python\n# Current (buggy):\nif \".executing\" in f.name and f.is_file():\n\n# Fix:\nname = f.name\nif \".executing\" in name and \".completed\" not in name and \".done\" not in name and \".failed\" not in name and f.is_file():\n```\n\n## Root Cause\nThe string `.executing` matches completed task files like `.executing.completed.done`, incorrectly flagging them as stalled.\n\n## Success Criteria"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":10,"aggregated":"---\ntask_id: high-1772671400\npriority: high\ncreated: 2026-03-05T19:10:00-05:00\nsource: hourly-reflection\n---\n\n# Task: Apply Watchdog False-Positive Fix\n\n## Objective\nApply the 3-line fix to eliminate 35 false-positive stalled_warnings.\n\n## Bug Location\nFile: `scripts/ogedei-watchdog.py`\nLine: ~140\n\n## Fix\n```python\n# Current (buggy):\nif \".executing\" in f.name and f.is_file():\n\n# Fix:\nname = f.name\nif \".executing\" in name and \".completed\" not in name and \".done\" not in name and \".failed\" not in name and f.is_file():\n```\n\n## Root Cause\nThe string `.executing` matches completed task files like `.executing.completed.done`, incorrectly flagging them as stalled.\n\n## Success Criteria","cwd":"/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772760767445}}
